{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_11_02",
  "title": "白石沙季 2話 お姉ちゃんのノート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスの振り付け……参考になる本あるかしら\nやっぱり、学校の図書室より、図書館に行った方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dance choreography… I wonder if there are any helpful books.\nMaybe I should go to a proper library instead of the school one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4742.607084900001,
          "startTime": 11.0092737516
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11333.333333300001,
          "startTime": 17.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.0092737516
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "『高みを目指して』……ちょっと違うかなぁ……\n『血まみれに』……ううん、ホラーじゃないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Aiming for the Top”… not quite right…\n“Covered in Blood”… no‚ this isn’t horror…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.266666476,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6756.7796389,
          "startTime": 24.0234461149
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0234461149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あら、千紗も来ていたのね\n歌詞作り中かしら。いいフレーズは浮かんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Chisa‚ you’re here too.\nWorking on lyrics? Come up with any good phrases?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4333331426
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0702273052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お姉ちゃん。えっと……あはは\nそれなりには順調かな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Saki. Um… haha.\nIt’s going okay‚ I guess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9232203325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "書きたい言葉が沢山浮かんで、悩んじゃうことも\nあるんだけど。……お姉ちゃんはどんな感じ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I keep thinking of lots of words I want to use‚\nso I get stuck sometimes… How about you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5108143967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私も、今のところ順調よ。完成した初稿を\n{user}さんに見てもらってるところなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m doing well so far too. I’ve finished a first draft‚\nand {user}-san is looking it over now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6813362282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～！？　もう初稿が完成したの？\nやっぱりお姉ちゃんは凄いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat!? You already finished a draft?\nYou really are amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5200459056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.1746694089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "自分のことだと、言葉にしやすいみたい\n伝えたい想いが、どんどん溢れてきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s easier to put things into words when it’s about myself.\nThe feelings I want to convey just kept overflowing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8666652044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "実際の歌詞も、一度書き始めたらするすると浮かんで\nきて、思っていたよりスムーズに完成させられたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once I started writing‚ the lyrics came naturally‚\nand I finished more smoothly than I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3666652044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.0083429814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃん、もうそこまで進んでるんだ……）\n（どうしよう、私はまだ完成には程遠いや）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saki is already that far ahead…）\n（What should I do… I’m nowhere near finished.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（つい順調って言っちゃったけど、全然まとまってないし）\n（もし遅れたら、作曲家さんにも迷惑を掛けちゃうよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I said it was going okay‚ but it’s not coming together at all.）\n（If I fall behind‚ I’ll cause trouble for the composer…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3386154652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "（……ううん。今までもこういう時に慌てちゃってたけど）\n（コツコツ頑張れば、道は開けたよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…No. I’ve panicked like this before‚ but…）\n（when I kept working steadily‚ things worked out.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.7664383412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "（うん。だから落ち着いて……大丈夫）\n（ゆっくりでもいいから、私らしく頑張ろう……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yeah. So stay calm… it’ll be okay.）\n（Even if it’s slow‚ I’ll do it my way…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7297036331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……？　もし行き詰まったりしたら\nいつでも相談してね？　私も手伝うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa…? If you get stuck‚\nyou can always talk to me. I’ll help you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7021071911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも行き詰まってるってほどじゃないから\nもう少しだけ自分で頑張ってみるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. But I’m not that stuck‚\nso I’ll try a little longer on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.3709277947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そう、分かったわ。でも……\n……ううん、なんでもない。応援してるわよ、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ alright. But…\n…No‚ it’s nothing. I’m rooting for you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4411786238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4411786119
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4411786119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、どうしたのかしら？\nもう家を出る時間なのに、全然起きてこないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wonder what’s wrong with Chisa?\nIt’s time to leave‚ but she’s not up at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.5333318711,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.3358128000045,
          "startTime": 158.0666676839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9242412089
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5999985378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "わあああああああ！　が、学校に遅れちゃう！\nあっ、お、お姉ちゃん、おはよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaahhh! I-I’m going to be late for school!\nOh—g-good morning‚ Saki!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.942554299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "こら千紗、家の中で走らないの！　もう……\nでも、寝坊なんてめずらしいわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ don’t run inside the house! Honestly…\nStill‚ it’s unusual for you to oversleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.8999893825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.5406239985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……寝る前に歌詞を考えてたら\nつい夜更かししちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… I was thinking about lyrics before bed‚\nand ended up staying up too late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7666529973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.1556807039
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
